# Automotive CAN Dashboard 🚗

## Overview
This project simulates an automotive ECU network and displays real-time vehicle telemetry.

## Features
- Simulated CAN data (Speed, RPM, Temperature)
- Live dashboard using Streamlit
- Multi-ECU visualization
- Real-time updates

## Architecture
Laptop Simulation → CAN Data → Dashboard

## Tech Used
- Python
- Streamlit
- CAN simulation concepts

## Future Work
- Integrate STM32 hardware
- Real CAN communication
- Diagnostics module

